PN,30401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FPatients given an "immune reset"
OL,7,Ftreatment on the NHS have gone into
OL,8,Fremission in "groundbreaking" new
OL,9,Ffindings.
OL,11,FFor the first time in the UK, people
OL,12,Fwith severe lupus have been treated
OL,13,Fwith CAR T-cell therapy, which experts
OL,14,Fbelieve may also work for illnesses
OL,15,Fsuch as multiple sclerosis.
OL,17,FThe therapy ` which only needs to be
OL,18,Fgiven once ` could revolutionise
OL,19,Ftreatment and remove the need for
OL,20,Flifelong medication.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@`O]pD@NOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FUntil now, it has only been offered to
OL,7,Fcancer patients on the NHS, where it
OL,8,Fhas shown huge success.
OL,10,FThe therapy works by genetically
OL,11,Fmodifying cells to enable the body's
OL,12,Fown immune system to recognise and
OL,13,Fattack problem cells, offering people
OL,14,Fthe chance of a cure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FIn the new NHS trial, led by
OL,7,FUniversity College London Hospitals
OL,8,FNHS Foundation Trust (UCLH) and
OL,9,FUniversity College London (UCL), five
OL,10,Fout of six patients with severe lupus
OL,11,Fwent into remission within a few
OL,12,Fmonths of receiving CAR-T.
OL,14,FOver an average follow-up of 11
OL,15,Fmonths, they experienced rapid
OL,16,Fimprovements in markers of the
OL,17,Fdisease, including a stabilisation or
OL,18,Fimprovement in their kidney function,
OL,19,Fwhich had been damaged by lupus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FLupus is a chronic autoimmune disease
OL,7,Fin which the immune system attacks
OL,8,Fhealthy tissues, causing widespread
OL,9,Finflammation and damage to organs such
OL,10,Fas the kidneys, lungs and heart.
OL,12,FIt can range from mild to severe, with
OL,13,Fsymptoms including joint pain, skin
OL,14,Fproblems, fatigue and inflammation of
OL,15,Fmajor organs.
OL,17,FAround 69,000 people in the UK are
OL,18,Fthought to have the condition, which
OL,19,Fmostly affects women.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FProfessor Karl Peggs, director of
OL,7,FUCLH's biomedical research centre,
OL,8,Ftold the Press Association that CAR-T
OL,9,Fcould offer people the chance of a
OL,10,Fcure, although bigger studies were
OL,11,Fneeded.
OL,13,F"These findings are truly
OL,14,Fgroundbreaking and offer fresh hope to
OL,15,Fpeople living with lupus," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,F"While more research is needed, the
OL,7,Fpossibility that CAR T-cell therapy
OL,8,Fcould deliver an immune reset and
OL,9,Fpotentially free patients from the
OL,10,Fcycle of chronic autoimmune disease
OL,11,Fmarks a remarkable step forward.
OL,13,F"If these results are confirmed in
OL,14,Flarger studies, the prospect of a cure
OL,15,Ffor lupus may no longer be out of
OL,16,Freach."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FDr Claire Roddie, an investigator on
OL,7,Fthe trial from UCL Cancer Institute
OL,8,Fand a UCLH consultant haematologist,
OL,9,Fsaid: "For patients living with severe
OL,10,Flupus that has not responded to
OL,11,Fexisting treatments, the options can
OL,12,Fbe very limited.
OL,14,F"These findings provide early evidence
OL,15,Fthat CAR T-cell therapy may be able to
OL,16,Freset the immune system and drive
OL,17,Fmeaningful clinical improvements after
OL,18,Fa single treatment.
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,F"Although these are still early days,
OL,7,Fthe results mark an important step
OL,8,Fforward in exploring how cellular
OL,9,Ftherapies could transform the
OL,10,Ftreatment of autoimmune diseases."
OL,12,FWith CAR-T, a person's own T cells,
OL,13,Fwhich are crucial for hunting out
OL,14,Finfected or damaged cells, are
OL,15,Fgenetically engineered by scientists
OL,16,Fand fed back into the patient via an
OL,17,Finfusion to "re-set" the immune system.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]yD@MOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FThe CAR-T in the trial was
OL,7,Fobecabtagene autoleucel (obe-cel),
OL,8,Fdeveloped by UCL spinout firm Autolus
OL,9,FTherapeutics.
OL,11,FObe-cel is designed to target and
OL,12,Fdeplete CD19-positive B cells, which
OL,13,Fplay a central role in lupus.
OL,15,FKatie Tinkler was forced to give up
OL,16,Fher job as a fitness instructor
OL,17,Fbecause of debilitating pain and
OL,18,Ffatigue caused by the severe lupus she
OL,19,Fhas had since she was 20.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FLupus caused her to suffer very
OL,7,Fswollen and painful joints, kidney
OL,8,Fdamage that meant she was close to
OL,9,Fneeding dialysis, lung and heart
OL,10,Fdisease, and a tendency to develop
OL,11,Fblood clots.
OL,13,FShe also suffered sepsis and multi-
OL,14,Forgan failure due to lupus, and was
OL,15,Fput in a coma in intensive care.
OL,17,FNow, the 52-year-old from Guildford,
OL,18,FSurrey, who is married to Simon and
OL,19,Fhas three children, Isabelle, 25,
OL,20,FEvie, 21, and Zac, 19, is in remission
OL,21,Fthanks to CAR-T she had at UCLH.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FShe told PA: "Thinking about how life
OL,7,Fwas for beforehand and how it is now,
OL,8,Fit's like night and day.
OL,10,F"My whole system was affected by lupus
OL,11,Fand my joints were so painful that
OL,12,Fsometimes I couldn't walk. I couldn't
OL,13,Fuse my hands to pick up mugs.
OL,15,F"My kidneys, heart and lungs were all
OL,16,Fgetting worse. But now I don't have
OL,17,Fthese problems any more."
OL,26,@nD@NOUrD@AOUwD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FAsked what she can do now that she
OL,7,Fcould not before, she said: "I have
OL,8,Fbeen skiing for the first time in a
OL,9,Fdecade. For the last 10 years we've
OL,10,Fgone skiing as a family but I haven't
OL,11,Fphysically even left the apartment.
OL,13,F"This January I skied for the first
OL,14,Ftime in 10 years ... I was arms out,
OL,15,Fhead to the sky and 'Oh my god'.
OL,17,F"The skiing was phenomenal, and to be
OL,18,Fable to participate ... it was
OL,19,Fmassive. It was a symbol.
OL,26,@oD@]OUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,F"My youngest child, he's 20 this year,
OL,7,Fso for 10 years now he can't remember
OL,8,Fme previously. My children can't
OL,9,Fremember me participating in things
OL,10,Fbefore now."
OL,12,FMrs Tinkler said she can now park away
OL,13,Ffrom shops rather than thinking she
OL,14,Fneeds to park very close by.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FShe added: "Regularly for years, when
OL,7,Fthe kids were at school, I'd get up in
OL,8,Fmy pyjamas, drop them to school in my
OL,9,Fpyjamas, come back to bed, stay in
OL,10,Fbed, put the alarm on for 2.50pm, get
OL,11,Fup and go back, pick them up, and then
OL,12,Fsurvive til my husband came home. That
OL,13,Fwas my life for years...
OL,15,F"After treatment, it was my daughter's
OL,16,Fwedding and I was up at 6am getting
OL,17,Fready.
OL,26,@nD@LOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,F"I didn't even see the guests in the
OL,7,Fevening because I was on the dance
OL,8,Ffloor the whole time. A year before,
OL,9,Fthat would have been completely
OL,10,Fdifferent day."
OL,12,FMrs Tinkler has been able to come off
OL,13,Fall steroid treatment and the other
OL,14,Fcocktail of drugs that were keeping
OL,15,Fher alive.
OL,17,FShe now takes just two tablets a day
OL,18,Fto prevent blood clots and keep her
OL,19,Fblood pressure low.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,F"It's miraculous for me," she said.
OL,7,F"My life two years ago versus now,
OL,8,Fit's unrecognisable.
OL,10,F"I feel blessed. I'm taking every gift
OL,11,Fthat UCLH and that trial has given me,
OL,12,Fand I'm running with it."
OL,14,FThe new study enrolled nine patients
OL,15,Faged 12 to 65 with active, severe
OL,16,Fdisease who had not responded to
OL,17,Fmultiple treatments for lupus.
OL,19,FMost were affected by lupus nephritis,
OL,20,Fa serious complication involving the
OL,21,Fkidneys.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@YO]oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FSix patients received a lower dose of
OL,7,FCAR-T while three were given a higher
OL,8,Fdose so results could be compared.
OL,10,FFollowing infusion, patients showed
OL,11,Fstrong expansion of CAR-T cells and
OL,12,Fdeep depletion of problem B cells.
OL,14,FOver time, B cells began to return,
OL,15,Ftypically between three and six
OL,16,Fmonths, but were predominantly early-
OL,17,Fstage cells, rather than the more
OL,18,Fmature populations associated with
OL,19,Fcausing issues in lupus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FResearchers said the findings show
OL,7,Fthat the therapy may be enabling an
OL,8,F"immune reset," rather than simply
OL,9,Fsuppressing the immune system.
OL,11,FThis is an important objective in
OL,12,Ftreating autoimmune diseases such as
OL,13,Flupus.
OL,15,FThe three patients on the higher dose
OL,16,Fhave only been followed up for three
OL,17,Fmonths so far, but experts believe
OL,18,Fthey could also achieve remission.
OL,19,FFive out of six patients given the
OL,20,Flower dose are already in remission.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30419
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781244253
OL,3,CPatients given 'immune reset'
OL,4,Ctreatment on NHS go into remission
OL,6,FThe new findings were presented at the
OL,7,FEULAR European Congress of
OL,8,FRheumatology in London last week.
OL,10,FLast year, biology teacher Emily
OL,11,FHenders became the first patient in
OL,12,Fthe UK to receive CAR-T to treat
OL,13,Fmultiple sclerosis. Experts are yet to
OL,14,Freport her results.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
